The paper deals with Open Information Extraction (OpenIE) methods and Knowledge Bases (KBs), which are commonly studied in the fields of natural language processing (NLP), artificial intelligence (AI), and databases (DB). The proposed approach also involves embedding techniques, which are often used in machine learning (ML) and deep learning (DL) research. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DB (Databases), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
